  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 180&deg;C/ 160&deg;C (fan)/ 350&deg;F/ Gas 4</p>\r\n<p>Drain the <strong>tinned</strong>&nbsp;<strong>lentils</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/lentil-kofta-harissa-and-feta-wraps/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mash the drained&nbsp;<strong>lentils</strong>&nbsp;in a flat-bottomed bowl (a pot is perfect!) to form a smooth paste</p>\r\n<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>ras el hanout</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>panko&nbsp;breadcrumbs</strong>,<strong>&nbsp;</strong>crack in the <strong>egg</strong>&nbsp;and add a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix well until the <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> are fully combined &ndash; this is your <strong>kofta mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/lentil-kofta-harissa-and-feta-wraps/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>kofta mixture</strong> into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span>&nbsp;and shape into balls</p>\r\n<p>Press each ball into a sausage shape, and then flatten&nbsp;into a rectangular patty &ndash; these are your <strong>koftas</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/lentil-kofta-harissa-and-feta-wraps/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick)&nbsp;with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>koftas</strong> and cook for 2 min on each side, or until they're crisp</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/lentil-kofta-harissa-and-feta-wraps/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, shred the <strong>little gem</strong>&nbsp;<strong>lettuce</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/lentil-kofta-harissa-and-feta-wraps/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>mayonnaise</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>harissa paste&nbsp;</strong>(Can't handle the heat? Go easy!)&nbsp;in a bowl</p>\r\n<p>Add a drizzle of&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong> and mix well &ndash; this is your <strong>harissa mayo</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/lentil-kofta-harissa-and-feta-wraps/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>tortilla wraps</strong>&nbsp;to a baking tray and place them in the oven for 2-3 min until they're warmed through</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/lentil-kofta-harissa-and-feta-wraps/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Assemble the wraps like this: <strong>wrap</strong>, <strong>shredded&nbsp;lettuce</strong>, <strong>kofta</strong>, <strong>harissa mayo</strong>, <strong>crumbled feta</strong> and <strong>sliced&nbsp;shallot</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
